<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>It is VERY clear that for the comment to be racistthat &quot;these problems&quot; must refer to racial issues.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
